The battle is nowhere near the CF, Logo. Even if it was, the CF's sound and 
shock absorbers would kinda prevent Battera from knowing there was a battle.

::Firearm::

Firearm hits a bump, flying through the air slightly, the missiles hitting 
him in the front, leaving charred dents. The optic blasts hits him in the 
cannon as his threads once again touch ground, the Maximal riding at full 
speed at Injector, his missile launcher firing a missile at the Pred.
